31b920.png\"/> đi với <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/e3ed6605-baa5-4238-8ffb-98bc0e1619be.png\"/> là sai).<br>\nĐáp án B: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/507a1dff-c837-4d0e-80f2-ad77e8535fae.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/df0bb56b-7bd0-4552-bb04-0d9c736019fa.png\"/> (<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/16cf30ef-43a6-4d85-8389-6385bcfda98c.png\"/> đi với <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/4fd56ca6-882c-4377-96d6-0c735216404a.png\"/> là sai).<br>\nĐáp án C: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/b8a1224d-73c2-4422-acf1-025fa2e11657.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/db5c2019-6bf4-4699-a1ec-efcc8f3a375e.png\"/>.<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/33721e6d-9462-4e0d-bbd5-60250093620a.png\"/> tương ứng <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/202047b4-79f4-4fb5-9be6-0e145c2e830c.png\"/> (Đúng).<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/2c27f21b-6455-411f-8791-db67f9582096.png\"/> tương ứng <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/71869aca-bd25-4e4b-b18a-30bbe915ddab.png\"/> (Đúng).<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/94358d4c-5a3f-479b-ab2c-eb3d5696168f.png\"/> tương ứng <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/c3b6138f-f5c9-48cc-a465-03928aff94d1.png\"/> (Đúng).<br>\nĐáp án D: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/394bed24-0eb4-4145-9762-1d0a7a4d2fc3.png\"